node.text:
When I had the idea to create @honest (over a decade ago 🤯), I wanted to focus on the health and safety of people, but also #MotherEarth ♻️ From day 1️⃣, we’ve focused on product efficacy, formula integrity & ingredient quality - packaging is the next step in our journey of constantly trying to do better and be better. 

After many years in the works, I’m beyond stoked for @honest_beauty’s glow up ✨ - one that represents our values as a brand and our vision for the future. Clean. Conscious. Culture.™️ Where we care about people 👫🏽 and the planet 🌏 - all day, every day. Everything and everyone has been considered. Because that’s what we’ve always, and will always be about ❣️

Safe ingredients that really work 💯 Made with sustainability in mind 🌱 Showing the world that wellness is for everyone 👫🏽👩🏻‍🤝‍👨🏿👩🏼‍🤝‍👨🏻 It’s more than a moment. It’s a movement - to inspire everyone to love living consciously. Come join us 💚#CleanConsciousCulture #PeopleAndThePlanet

node.text:
Happy #InternationalWomensDay! 💗💗 This year’s theme is all about choosing to challenge. We’re all responsible for our own thoughts and actions all day, every day - and we should be choosing to empower women and smash stereotypes ‼️ Did you know 73% of women experience bias at work? Totally not acceptable. Did you know that only 37 companies in the Fortune 500 are run by women? Or, did you know that only 34% of Fortune 500 board seats are held by women and minorities? This needs to change.

Clearly, we’ve all got a lot of work to do. At The Honest Company, we’re determined to continue supporting our female workforce so that they feel safe and empowered - both professionally and personally. 68% of our workforce are women and 59% of our leadership team are women - women are at the core of everything we do! 👊🏽👊🏽

This year, I wanted to challenge myself, my @honest + @honest_beauty fam & YOU to call out gender bias and inequity when you see it. Join us as we #ChooseToChallenge ✋🏽 #IWD2021 #IWD

#TutorialTuesday - It’s so important to remember to take care of yourself, whatever way you see fit. For me, it’s all about the little things, like my sweet Hayesie Boo helping me make my fave matcha morning smoothie 💚 It’s super quick + easy and only includes 5 ingredients. Plus, the clean up is so simple, even a 3-year-old can handle it 🙌🏽🎉

INGREDIENTS: 
12 oz. Coconut Water - @harmlessharvest 
1 tbsp Almond Macadamia Be Well Blend - @wild_friends x @bewellbykelly
1 tsp Matcha Powder - @aiyamatcha
1 Whole Peeled Banana 
1 scoop Vanilla Grass-Fed Beef Protein Powder - @bewellbykelly 

DIRECTIONS: 
Add all of your ingredients into your blender and get it goin’! @blendtec 
Add about cup of ice to your mixture + blend together 
& your smoothie is ready to enjoy! 
Last step - some easy clean up @honest

node.text: Still buzzing from my time with the one and only former President @barackobama. Want to experience exceptional empathy, warmth and wisdom from a true leader and awesome human? Spend 5 minutes with this man. Check out our chat about his insightful and inspiring new book 📖 #APromisedLand. It's the perfect holiday gift for just about everyone in your family! We also chatted all the things, including potty training...yes, I actually spoke to President Obama about potty training my son 🤦🏽‍♀️

node.text:
As a young kid, I saw lots of boys and girls in my neighborhood who looked like me. However, in Hollywood and entertainment, I never saw anyone that I felt represented me. There was never anyone holding open any doors or offering guidance - instead, it was me knocking through doors basically doing everything I could just to be given a shot. As a result, I've committed my life and career to supporting the needs of our community as they pertain to business, health + wellness, opportunities, and most importantly, representation. I believe that if we are all unidos and show up as a community, we will be the change we want to see for ourselves, for our children, and for many generations to come. 

Gracias for including me in this incredible and humbling event @hispanicheritage ❤️ with all the amazing winners. Please visit www.HispanicHeritage.org to read more. 

Que viva la causa, viva la raza, y viva la unidad ✊🏽 #HispanicHeritageMonth

One of my passions is home design - I just love transforming spaces. 🥰Earlier this year, I spent a couple of weeks at home with my parents (sleeping in a teenage sized bunk bed) and realized they definitely needed an upgrade! 💯

So I talked to my homegirl @lizzymathis & it went like this ⤵️

Me: I have an idea! 😄
Lizzy: Uh oh! 😳
Me: Let’s redo my parent’s house 🏡 
Lizzy: Really, are your parents down? 🤔
Me: Probably not but let’s do it anyway! 😜

And the rest is history! Check out their home design upgrade at the link in profile. @cathyalba may or may not have been into it! 😉💖

node.text:
#MondayMotivation - sending my girl @allysonfelix all the good energy today! ⚡️⚡️ Did you know Allyson is tied for the most Olympic medals in athletics history - she has 9️⃣‼️ & today, she’s stepping into the @olympics Stadium in Tokyo to complete in her 5️⃣th Olympic Games - but her first as a mama🤱🏾. While Allyson is straight up one of the most decorated athletes ever 🏆🏆, she is also one of the deepest, kindest, inspirational and charismatic humans off the field. She has accomplished so many things, but she has really stepped up for women and athletes who have chosen to have families - she’s changed the game for so many! 👊🏽 Allyson, you radiate so much light, determination, and love and I feel so grateful we have connected. Shine bright mama - blind them with your goodness ✨🤍🤗!

When you’re watching Allyson tonight, some of her words to marinate on: “So when you see me on the track, I hope you understand my fight. As an athlete who was told I was too old, as a mother who was told to know my place, as a mother who wasn’t sure I would live to raise my daughter. I hope you see that for me, it’s about so much more than what the clock says” - Allyson Felix 💗💗💗. Yes it is my friend we have your back 👊🏽!

Clearly I’m just a liiiittle bit excited for my kids to go back to school 🙈 Anyone else?! 

On the real though - a round of applause for our teachers 👏🏽👏🏽👏🏽 They always show up & I am eternally grateful for everything they do ❤️ BUT did you know 92% of teachers pay out-of-pocket for classroom supplies - including cleaning + disinfecting products?! Not cool. So it’s time to show up for them ‼️ Send your kiddo back to school with a full kit to ensure their teacher has everything they need to keep their classroom + hands sanitized ✅ 

Additionally, for every “stay safe” essential purchase, @honest is teaming up with @baby2baby to provide a hand sanitizer to a student in need ✨ Let’s tackle this next school year safely + together 📚✏️📓 #HonestlyBackToSchool
